<!--
=========================
Features
=========================
- Uses OpenTok API to provide a videochat room
- Single chat room requires embed url (can be obtained from:
   http://www.tokbox.com/opentok/plugnplay/basicembed)
- Multi room chat requires an API key/secret (can be obtained from:
   http://www.tokbox.com/opentok/api/documentation/gettingstarted#getAPIKeyhttp)
- List of available chat rooms (based on elgg access controls)
- Rooms will automatically be removed after 24 hours (not tested)
- Can also be used by non-loggedin users (Join Only)
- Chat can be popped out into a separate window

=========================
Version Information
=========================
0.1 (2011-09-14):
	- first release

